<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="robots" content="index, follow, noimageindex">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>A. O. Asare</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; max-width: 950px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 30px; color: #222; line-height: 1.7; }
    nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-bottom: 18px; margin-bottom: 60px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
    .nav-name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; }
    .nav-links a { margin-left: 22px; text-decoration: none; color: #333; }
    .nav-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .main { display: flex; gap: 55px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .photo { width: 260px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; }
    .content { max-width: 560px; }
    h1 { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 0; }
    a { color: #1a5fb4; }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      nav, .main { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      .nav-links a { margin-left: 0; margin-right: 14px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<nav>
  <div class="nav-name">A. O. Asare</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="index.html">Home</a>
    <a href="research.html">Research</a>
    <a href="working-papers.html">Working Papers</a>
    <a href="teaching.html">Teaching</a>
    <a href="contacts.html">Contacts</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<main class="main">
  <img src="photo.png" alt="" class="photo">

  <section class="content">
    <h1>A. O. Asare</h1>

    <p>
      I am a researcher in economics. My work focuses on development economics,
      energy economics, educational aid effectiveness, climate policy, and
      applied microeconometrics.
    </p>

    <p>
      My research examines how policy design, institutional quality, and economic
      constraints shape welfare, education, energy access, and development
      outcomes.
    </p>

  </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
